Disable comments on pages that are relative to the root URL like `http://example.com/about`. Requires [comment][link:../reference/extension/comment] extension.

~~~ .php
<?php if ($site->has('parent')): ?>
<?php Shield::get('comments'); ?>
<?php endif; ?>
~~~